files.description: Documentation explaining the ID scheme, file formats, how the checker works, and how to run the demo to generate the human-readable report under runtime/outputs/_build/.

missionDescription: Implement an ID system + mismatch checker that links (a) extraction rows, (b) taxonomy annotations (JSONL), and (c) prereg fields; include a demo that intentionally triggers an ID mismatch and outputs a human-readable report to runtime/outputs/_build/.
missionSuccessCriteria: Complete strategic task identified by Meta-Coordinator or escalated by Strategic Tracker
Even with templates and schema, the project will fail if identifiers drift; goal_21 is the glue that prevents un-joinable datasets and silent inconsistencies.
